  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add grated carrots and stir-fry for about 5 minutes until they start to soften slightly.",
    "Stir in onion, garlic, cumin seeds, turmeric powder, salt, pepper, and red chili flakes. Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
    "Reduce heat to low and cover the skillet with a lid. Cook for about 10 more minutes until the carrots are soft and golden brown on top.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro if desired."
